             was indicted for <rs id="t18320705-235-off1236" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320705-235-off1236" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320705-235-off1236" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320705-235-cd1237" type="crimeDate">29th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-235-off1236 t18320705-235-cd1237"></join>, 1 bridle, value 5s., and 1 pad, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320705-235-victim1960" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     James
                  <interp inst="t18320705-235-victim1960" type="surname" value="James"></interp>
